        <!-- Optional: URL for more information about this update -->
        <url>https://github.com/SmartmindTech/SM_Estratoos_plugin/releases/tag/v2.0.17</url>

        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.17 - Prevent Storyline Navigation Revert</h3>

            <h4>Improvements</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Intercept suspend_data WRITES (LMSSetValue/SetValue) in addition to reads</li>
                <li>Prevents Storyline from reverting slide position after navigation</li>
                <li>First 3 writes are intercepted and modified to maintain target slide</li>
                <li>Works with both SCORM 1.2 and SCORM 2004</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Problem: Storyline reads modified suspend_data but writes back internal state</li>
                <li>Solution: Intercept SetValue calls and re-apply slide modification</li>
                <li>MAX_WRITE_INTERCEPTS = 3 to allow eventual normal operation</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.16: URL-based slide navigation (?slide=X) for embed</li>
                <li>v2.0.15: LMSGetValue interception for navigation</li>
                <li>v2.0.14: Progress tracking & suspend_data enhancements</li>
                <li>v2.0.12: Rise 360 navigation & notification fix</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
    </update>
</updates>
